high_descs: Turn to the left to face the sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap from in between the sinks.
Take the soap and move a step to the right.
Place the soap in the sink and turn the water on. Turn it off and pick up the soap again.
Hold the soap and take a step to the left.
Place the soap on the counter in between the sinks.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off the soap and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn to your right and face the vanity
Pick up the bar of soap that is in between the sinks
Turn around and take a step, turn left and take a step, the turn left and face the right sink
Place the soap in the right sink then turn on the sink.  Turn off the sink and pick up the soap
Take a step to your left
Place the soap on the counter in between the two sinks to the right of the bottle of soap
anns.task_desc: Place wet soap on a counter

high_descs: Turn left and face toward the bathroom counter between the sinks
Pick up the soap bar from the bathroom counter
Move slightly right then turn left to face the sink
Rinse the soap under water in the sink then remove it
Move slightly left then turn right to face the counter
Put the soap bar on the counter just right of the pump bottle
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed soap on the bathroom counter

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the bathroom counter.
Pick up the bar of soap that is to the right of the lotion dispenser on the counter.
Move over to the sink basin on the far right of the bathroom counter.
Place the soap in the sink and rinse it off before pulling it back out.
Move back over to the lotion dispenser on the bathroom counter.
Place the bar of soap down on the counter to the right of the lotion dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap back on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right to face the sink counter.
Pick up the bar of soap that is in front of the toilet paper on the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again to face the rightmost sink.
Put the bar of soap into the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the bar of soap from the sink basin.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Place the clean bar of soap on the front edge of the counter to the left of the rightmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the soap on the counter.
Pick up the soap on the counter.
Bring the soap to the sink on the right.
Wet the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the wet soap to the counter left of that sink.
Put the soap on that counter.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the counter.
